{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_540.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Welcome to Linca and Ayesha's Cooking Class! Today's assignment is to make an egg wrap dish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Marion likes egg dishes, as well. I need to learn this, no matter what!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "This time, let's pay attention to its looks, too. If it looks good, it'll taste good, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What an ultimate secret...!<CR>I need to remember that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Decorating the appearance will somehow make it taste better. I learned a useful tip."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Now, let's start cooking!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Uhh...umm, this is...<CR>It might be a failure..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes. It is completely different from the ones I always see being served on dining tables."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Maybe it is impossible for me to cook after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Y-You can't give up yet.<CR>We just...need a change of plans!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Scrambled eggs are easier to make.<CR>If you think it won't work out,<CR>then just switch gears in the middle!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Try to find a way out of extreme difficulties... Even against great adversity, one must never give up..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "There is a strategy based on those very tactics. So, it is the same!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yes, so let's give it a try!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, this is...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Umm...it used to be a scrambled egg..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Although, that was only for a brief moment. The fire was way too strong..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "So it seems. There is no more evidence that it used to be eggs. It now looks more like...charcoal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But, but, but...it still might be okay if we add some color to it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "...Color? But it is brown."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Umm, umm...then how about this flag?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Ooh! A flag on a dish...<CR>It looks so impressive...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, so there is a skill like this in cooking..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Putting a flag on a dish will kind of make it look good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I learned a lot! I shall remember this as a last resort!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "However, this is almost equal to a<CR>waving a white flag in surrender...<CR>I must try to avoid it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm...I think I gave her the wrong idea. Teaching is hard...)"
        }
    ]
}